&lt;h2 id=&#34;execute-a-task&#34;&gt;Execute a task&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code&gt;pytask&lt;/code&gt; in your terminal, and it will automatically collect and execute all tasks.&lt;/p&gt;


















